  - POST /api/studios/:studioId/promos/apply [200] — apply promo (body: code)
  - POST /api/studios/:studioId/billing/contact [200] — update billing contact
  - POST /webhooks/payment-provider [200] — receive provider events

- Security:
  - Authentication: JWT or session-based. Every billing endpoint requires a valid studio-level token and user identity.
  - Authorization: Role-based checks: only users with roles Owner or Billing/Finance Admin can mutate subscriptions/payment methods and view full invoice PDFs; other roles can view limited billing summary.
